Class JsonFeed

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.micronaut.rss.jsonfeed.JsonFeed

  • @Introspected
public class JsonFeed
extends java.lang.Object
    A JSON Feed is a list that may change over time, and the individual items in the list may change..

    2.2.0
    Author:
